      <title>黄金签证改造的诱惑富裕到新西兰作为避风港</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/golden-visa-revamp-tempts-wealthy-to-eye-new-zealand-as-haven</link>
      <description><![CDATA[移民部长埃里卡·斯坦福（Erica Stanford）说，随着地缘政治紧张局势的上升促使富人考虑国外的选择，新西兰正在对其对美国和欧洲进行改造的黄金签证计划的“红热”兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/golden-visa-revamp-tempts-wealthy-to-eye-new-zealand-as-haven</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为什么法国最右边取决于海军陆战队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/marine-le-pen-why-french-far-right-depends-on-national-rally-leader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对挪用公款的海军陆战队的定罪很可能破坏了她在2027年取代伊曼纽尔·马克龙（Emmanuel Macron）担任法国总统的机会，并在面对不确定的未来的领导下离开了该国的主要反对派，这是该国的主要反对派。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/marine-le-pen-why-french-far-right-depends-on-national-rally-leader</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 17:40:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
