    <item>
      <title>当交易者权衡特朗普对俄罗斯原油的威胁时，石油的进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-march-31</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）建议美国可能努力减少俄罗斯的原油运输之后，石油上升了，俄罗斯是世界第三大生产商和主要出口商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-march-31</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 23:20:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着官员寻求资金，纽约市运输工人的攻击被击落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/nyc-transit-assaults-down-as-officials-seek-federal-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，对纽约市的地铁和公共汽车工人的袭击下降了31％，这是过境官员在致运输部门的一封信中引用的统计数据，以避免威胁性的联邦资金削减。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/nyc-transit-assaults-down-as-officials-seek-federal-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 20:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
